## Attribution

This project is based on the original Igris implementation by Keyvan Kambakhsh.
Original repository: https://github.com/keyvank/Igris

The original work is licensed under the MIT License and has been enhanced with:
- Multi-modal training capabilities (text, code, image prompt generation)
- Task-aware tokenization system
- JSONL dataset format support
- Enhanced documentation and examples
- Improved project structure and organization

We acknowledge and thank the original author for the foundational work that made this enhanced version possible.